    <h4 class="odd">DESCRIPTION</h4> <br>

    <p class="even"></p>

    <p>WF-Channel is an easy to use module for Xoops (ver 2.0.5 and higher) to create information pages. </p>

    <p>
        It is a way of managing those pages of information that other modules just don't seem to fit.<BR>You can keep
        together those 'About Us', 'Refer a Friend', 'Link to Us', Privacy Statements <BR>or
        just about any type of information that you believe would benefit your users. <BR>This module is
        therefore kept simple but still offers a lot of interesting options.
    </p>

    <p>
        <br> <br>

        <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><B>Here is a short selection of features offered:</B></span>
    </p>

    <p>
        <span style="font-size: x-small;">
    <ul>
        <li>easy to use module.</li>
        <li>allows you to create pages using Xoops codes/smilies and/or HTML tags.</li>
        <li>simple builtin editor or use of Spaw editor if installed.*</li>
        <li>allows to import html documents.</li>
        <li>allows to add images.</li>
        <li>option to define a publish and expiry date if needed.</li>
        <li>...</li>
    </ul>
    </span>
    </p>

